00:10:51,109 --> 00:10:52,069
without the adults?

281
00:10:52,429 --> 00:10:53,669
Why do you come here

282
00:10:53,669 --> 00:10:54,749
without the adults?

283
00:10:57,229 --> 00:10:58,469
Naughty boy.

284
00:10:58,829 --> 00:11:00,349
He promised to buy me a meal.

285
00:11:00,709 --> 00:11:02,109
My mother is waiting outside.

286
00:11:04,469 --> 00:11:06,069
It seems you get along quite well.

287
00:11:06,349 --> 00:11:07,669
Thanks to your help.

288
00:11:10,829 --> 00:11:11,709
Lin Xi.

289
00:11:12,749 --> 00:11:14,749
Can you give us the toys

290
00:11:14,749 --> 00:11:15,749
in your hands?

291
00:11:17,309 --> 00:11:17,989
This...

292
00:11:20,669 --> 00:11:21,949
I will give them to you if you want.

293
00:11:22,789 --> 00:11:23,589
Thank you, Xi.

294
00:11:23,589 --> 00:11:24,429
Hey.

295
00:11:24,629 --> 00:11:25,349
You can't take them.

296
00:11:26,829 --> 00:11:28,109
These toys are so cute.

297
00:11:28,109 --> 00:11:29,069
Here, take these.

298
00:11:29,229 --> 00:11:31,749
Look at the toys. They are awfully made.

299
00:11:32,029 --> 00:11:33,789
We want that two.

300
00:11:33,789 --> 00:11:35,149
I just like them very much.

301
00:11:35,149 --> 00:11:36,269
She just offered to give it to you.

302
00:11:36,269 --> 00:11:37,749
Didn't you reject it?

303
00:11:38,109 --> 00:11:39,229
I'm taking it now.

304
00:11:39,789 --> 00:11:41,749
Why is the change?

305
00:11:42,149 --> 00:11:43,789
I want to give it to Wang Dong.

306
00:11:43,789 --> 00:11:44,749
Wang Dong likes it.

307
00:11:45,229 --> 00:11:46,829
Lin Xi likes it too.

308
00:11:51,149 --> 00:11:53,109
I'm not going to argue with grown-ups.

309
00:11:53,189 --> 00:11:53,869
Let's leave.

310
00:12:02,869 --> 00:12:03,949
Oh my.

311
00:12:04,709 --> 00:12:05,389
Why did you fight

312
00:12:05,389 --> 00:12:06,829
over the toys with kids?

313
00:12:07,029 --> 00:12:08,549
Kids can't be spoiled.

314
00:12:08,549 --> 00:12:09,949
They must be taught how to show respect.

315
00:12:25,869 --> 00:12:26,509
Lin Xi.

316
00:12:29,429 --> 00:12:31,189
Why do you look anxious?

317
00:12:31,189 --> 00:12:31,869
Look at this.

318
00:12:32,389 --> 00:12:33,109
I've checked the link

319
00:12:33,109 --> 00:12:34,429
written on the ticket website.

320
00:12:34,429 --> 00:12:35,309
And I found something weird

321
00:12:35,309 --> 00:12:36,749
about the ticket website's
and the organizer's domain name.

322
00:12:37,109 --> 00:12:38,709
The webpage of the music festival
was weird too.

323
00:12:38,709 --> 00:12:39,669
I discovered

324
00:12:39,949 --> 00:12:41,109
that the link was a fake one.

325
00:12:41,309 --> 00:12:42,309
What do you mean?

326
00:12:43,069 --> 00:12:44,349
If I'm not wrong,

327
00:12:44,669 --> 00:12:46,149
the ticket for this music festival
is fake.

328
00:12:46,509 --> 00:12:47,589
Jiang Yimian got scammed.

329
00:12:47,749 --> 00:12:48,629
No way.

330
00:13:01,429 --> 00:13:02,549
What do we do now?

331
00:13:03,149 --> 00:13:05,349
Are you sure the music festival is fake?

332
00:13:05,749 --> 00:13:06,269
Lin Xi and I

333
00:13:06,269 --> 00:13:08,309
tried to call the organizer just now.

334
00:13:09,189 --> 00:13:10,149
No one answered it.

335
00:13:10,429 --> 00:13:12,109
Even the number is fake.

336
00:13:12,309 --> 00:13:13,909
The scammer is just bold.

337
00:13:15,189 --> 00:13:16,469
What do we do now?

338
00:13:17,309 --> 00:13:18,669
Why hesitate?

339
00:13:18,669 --> 00:13:19,629
Just tell her directly.

340
00:13:19,629 --> 00:13:20,469
Isn't it settled?

341
00:13:20,469 --> 00:13:21,549
Let's not be so direct.

342
00:13:22,189 --> 00:13:23,589
What if she can't come around
to the truth?

343
00:13:25,709 --> 00:13:27,189
I'm afraid two people will be harmed
by this.

344
00:13:27,549 --> 00:13:28,629
What do you mean?

345
00:13:28,989 --> 00:13:30,149
If she's upset,

346
00:13:30,349 --> 00:13:31,549
my heart breaks too.

347
00:13:33,029 --> 00:13:33,989
Don't be exaggerating.

348
00:13:34,509 --> 00:13:35,909
Still, we have to tell the truth.

349
00:13:39,989 --> 00:13:41,349
I think

350
00:13:42,629 --> 00:13:44,869
we can tell her in gradual stages.

351
00:13:46,629 --> 00:13:47,669
What do you mean?

352
00:13:49,669 --> 00:13:52,229
Plan A, remind her tactfully.

353
00:13:53,229 --> 00:13:54,709
Will it be possible

354
00:13:54,709 --> 00:13:56,269
that you fail to meet
someone you expected to see

355
00:13:56,269 --> 00:13:57,789
in the concert?

356
00:13:57,789 --> 00:13:58,949
Impossible.

357
00:13:58,949 --> 00:13:59,989
I will shove over to the front

358
00:13:59,989 --> 00:14:01,109
and I can see the band.

359
00:14:03,989 --> 00:14:05,349
There is always something unexpected
to occur, you know.

360
00:14:05,749 --> 00:14:07,509
What if your favorite band
doesn't show up?

361
00:14:07,509 --> 00:14:08,789
If so, I will watch the performance
of other bands.

362
00:14:08,789 --> 00:14:09,669
There are so many bands there.

363
00:14:09,669 --> 00:14:10,829
What if surprises happen.

364
00:14:12,789 --> 00:14:15,389
Plan B, hint her.

365
00:14:23,709 --> 00:14:24,869
The Magician card
is in reversed position.

366
00:14:25,389 --> 00:14:26,909
It indicates you have walked
in the wrong direction.

367
00:14:26,909 --> 00:14:28,189
Failure and scam.

368
00:14:28,589 --> 00:14:30,149
It means you can't attend

369
00:14:30,149 --> 00:14:31,629
the music festival.

370
00:14:31,829 --> 00:14:32,909
You read it from the opposite direction.

371
00:14:32,909 --> 00:14:34,309
It is not reversed from my view.

372
00:14:34,709 --> 00:14:36,029
Even the heavens help me.

373
00:14:36,229 --> 00:14:37,709
Everything must go smoothly.

374
00:14:41,269 --> 00:14:41,909
Good girl.

375
00:14:42,669 --> 00:14:44,629
The final plan, tell her directly.

376
00:14:50,229 --> 00:14:51,189
You scared me.

377
00:14:51,389 --> 00:14:52,629
There is something I need to tell you.

378
00:14:52,989 --> 00:14:53,989
The ticket is fake.

379
00:14:54,429 --> 00:14:55,149
It can't be fake

380
00:14:55,149 --> 00:14:56,149
even if you are fake.

381
00:14:56,149 --> 00:14:57,149
It's real that the ticket is fake.

382
00:14:57,149 --> 00:14:57,829
This ticket is fake for real.

383
00:14:57,829 --> 00:14:58,829
Even if you receive the ticket,

384
00:14:58,829 --> 00:14:59,469
it is still a fake one.

385
00:14:59,469 --> 00:15:00,749
Are you doing some sort
of tongue twister?

386
00:15:01,069 --> 00:15:02,109
What if I receive the ticket?

387
00:15:02,309 --> 00:15:03,309
The thunder will strike me down.

388
00:15:03,309 --> 00:15:03,949
Jiang Yimian.

389
00:15:04,189 --> 00:15:05,149
Here is your parcel.

390
00:15:05,429 --> 00:15:06,469
I got it for you.

391
00:15:06,469 --> 00:15:07,349
Thank you.

392
00:15:07,349 --> 00:15:08,549
It must be the ticket.

393
00:15:13,869 --> 00:15:15,309
It's my ticket.

394
00:15:15,309 --> 00:15:16,189
I got it.

395
00:15:16,589 --> 00:15:17,509
Look at this with your eyes, Xie Ang.

396
00:15:18,269 --> 00:15:19,869
The thunder is going to strike you down.

397
00:15:22,869 --> 00:15:25,549
Even the ticket is forged delicately.

398
00:15:27,029 --> 00:15:28,389
It costs 388 yuan.

399
00:15:28,669 --> 00:15:29,909
Of course it is.

400
00:15:33,640 --> 00:15:35,020
(Grade 2, Class 1)

401
00:15:35,989 --> 00:15:37,189
Quiet.

402
00:15:37,789 --> 00:15:39,229
Haven't you seen rain before?

403
00:15:39,229 --> 00:15:44,829
Power cut-off, please.
Class ends, please.

404
00:15:47,189 --> 00:15:48,629
The prayer does work.

405
00:15:51,149 --> 00:15:52,589
Stop making a fuss.

406
00:15:58,029 --> 00:15:58,549
Great.

407
00:15:58,549 --> 00:16:00,069
Perhaps the self-study session
will be cancelled.

408
00:16:00,189 --> 00:16:01,109
That's possible.

409
00:16:03,069 --> 00:16:04,709
You are too optimistic.

410
00:16:05,109 --> 00:16:05,949
I bet Mr. Xie

411
00:16:05,949 --> 00:16:08,029
will ask us to continue our study
with the torch on.

412
00:16:11,629 --> 00:16:12,949
Students who have torch lights,

413
00:16:13,309 --> 00:16:14,589
switch them on.

414
00:16:15,389 --> 00:16:17,349
I will go and check it out.

415
00:16:17,349 --> 00:16:18,069
Class representative.

416
00:16:18,309 --> 00:16:18,749
Jinx it.

417
00:16:18,749 --> 00:16:20,029
Look after the class.

418
00:16:20,029 --> 00:16:21,629
No problem. Don't worry.

419
00:16:26,389 --> 00:16:27,589
Students.

420
00:16:27,589 --> 00:16:29,389
The tea party begins.

421
00:16:31,109 --> 00:16:32,389
Keep your voice low.

422
00:16:32,389 --> 00:16:32,949
Hey.

423
00:16:32,949 --> 00:16:34,669
Don't you create grudges for me
and my father.

424
00:16:39,789 --> 00:16:40,949
What are you reading?

425
00:16:40,949 --> 00:16:42,069
It's the book you borrowed for me.

426
00:16:42,229 --> 00:16:43,029
Appreciation of Music.

427
00:16:52,309 --> 00:16:53,549
You shall advise her well.

428
00:16:58,589 --> 00:16:59,149
Hi.

429
00:16:59,149 --> 00:17:00,709
Mianmian, the ticket...

430
00:17:01,549 --> 00:17:03,029
If you dare say it is a fake ticket,

431
00:17:03,029 --> 00:17:04,109
our friendship ends here.

432
00:17:05,189 --> 00:17:06,789
No, I'm not.

433
00:17:07,149 --> 00:17:08,269
I bring you some flower seeds.

434
00:17:08,749 --> 00:17:10,029
I can unshell it for you.

435
00:17:10,429 --> 00:17:10,989
Sure.

436
00:17:14,549 --> 00:17:17,029
Huh? He is eating flower seeds now.

437
00:17:17,029 --> 00:17:19,309
Xie Ang is defeated.

438
00:17:34,789 --> 00:17:35,709
My old tablemate.

439
00:17:37,229 --> 00:17:39,069
How do you feel

440
00:17:39,069 --> 00:17:39,909
returning here?

441
00:17:40,389 --> 00:17:41,829
My new seat is just half a meter
from here though.

442
00:17:41,829 --> 00:17:43,349
It is not far at all.

443
00:17:49,189 --> 00:17:51,109
It has been some time
since we've had such a leisure time

444
00:17:51,109 --> 00:17:52,749
during the self-study session.

445
00:17:53,189 --> 00:17:54,389
It will be great

446
00:17:54,389 --> 00:17:56,549
to listen to a soothing song

447
00:17:57,509 --> 00:17:58,509
right now.

448
00:18:05,589 --> 00:18:07,309
Why did you take the phone out?

449
00:18:09,949 --> 00:18:10,589
Music?

450
00:18:11,109 --> 00:18:11,869
Sure.

451
00:18:27,749 --> 00:18:28,909
Oh, this song.

452
00:18:32,389 --> 00:18:33,109
It's nice, right?

453
00:18:34,029 --> 00:18:34,829
Yes.

454
00:18:38,029 --> 00:18:38,749
Hold on.

455
00:18:39,229 --> 00:18:40,869
I will build a soundproof environment

456
00:18:41,589 --> 00:18:43,949
with a surrounding sound.

457
00:18:45,366 --> 00:18:48,093
♪Your gentleness
is like the afternoon breeze♪

458
00:18:48,900 --> 00:18:50,626
♪Amongst the crowd♪

459
00:18:50,666 --> 00:18:53,240
♪My gaze remains on you♪

460
00:18:53,966 --> 00:18:55,886
♪As if I were watching the starry sky♪

461
00:18:55,933 --> 00:18:58,520
♪I can't help blushing♪

462
00:18:59,140 --> 00:19:03,260
♪She's got such a gentle demeanor♪

463
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:07,340
♪I'm not myself when talking to her♪

464
00:19:07,420 --> 00:19:10,180
♪Can I feel his heartbeat
at this very moment♪

465
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:12,553
♪And play the most romantic love song?♪

466
00:19:12,700 --> 00:19:14,893
♪Can I reach his heart♪

467
00:19:14,894 --> 00:19:17,566
♪With just one look?♪

468
00:19:17,910 --> 00:19:20,020
♪Should I tell her
that I'm noticing her too♪

469
00:19:20,286 --> 00:19:22,960
♪When she tries to
steal a glance at me again?♪

470
00:19:25,149 --> 00:19:26,549
Who did you write

471
00:19:27,909 --> 00:19:29,069
in that essay regarding your idol?

472
00:19:30,549 --> 00:19:32,669
It's not a particular person.

473
00:19:34,349 --> 00:19:35,149
Actually,

474
00:19:35,149 --> 00:19:36,469
I admire

475
00:19:36,469 --> 00:19:37,389
doctors very much.

476
00:19:38,109 --> 00:19:39,749
I want to go to Jinghua University

477
00:19:39,749 --> 00:19:41,149
because of its medical school.

478
00:19:44,549 --> 00:19:45,349
What about you?

479
00:19:46,229 --> 00:19:47,829
Which university do you want to go to?

480
00:19:50,509 --> 00:19:52,189
Dad, you asked for me?

481
00:19:52,789 --> 00:19:53,389
Have a seat.

482
00:19:57,389 --> 00:19:59,229
Get ready for this.

483
00:19:59,709 --> 00:20:01,669
Regarding the information
for applying to NIT,

484
00:20:01,669 --> 00:20:04,309
Mr. Chen has made a list for you.

485
00:20:04,420 --> 00:20:06,646
(Situ Institute of Technology)

486
00:20:08,189 --> 00:20:08,829
Dad.

487
00:20:10,869 --> 00:20:12,029
Must I go to this school?

488
00:20:13,229 --> 00:20:14,709
Situ's Business School

489
00:20:14,709 --> 00:20:16,229
is the world's top university.

490
00:20:17,149 --> 00:20:19,789
We need people with
a business education background

491
00:20:19,789 --> 00:20:20,989
in the industry

492
00:20:20,989 --> 00:20:22,029
of precision instruments.

493
00:20:22,749 --> 00:20:25,469
Even if you want to start up a business
in the future,

494
00:20:25,469 --> 00:20:27,829
the resource and background
of this school

495
00:20:27,829 --> 00:20:29,549
is a great help to you.

496
00:20:33,429 --> 00:20:34,349
I know.

497
00:20:35,229 --> 00:20:36,309
But

498
00:20:36,869 --> 00:20:38,109
I don't feel like studying overseas.

499
00:20:43,549 --> 00:20:44,269
Junxing.

500
00:20:45,429 --> 00:20:48,269
I thought we had reached a consensus

501
00:20:48,269 --> 00:20:50,149
on the NIT.

502
00:20:53,149 --> 00:20:54,429
I haven't made up my mind yet.

503
00:20:54,709 --> 00:20:55,829
No way.

504
00:20:55,949 --> 00:20:56,549
How could an ace student like you

505
00:20:56,549 --> 00:20:57,949
have no goals?

506
00:21:00,989 --> 00:21:02,469
Well.

507
00:21:05,349 --> 00:21:07,189
Though I'm not willing,
I will invite you to my school.

508
00:21:07,829 --> 00:21:09,309
Let's go to Jinghua University together.

509
00:21:12,229 --> 00:21:13,589
Invite me to your school?

510
00:21:15,549 --> 00:21:17,069
I need time to consider it.

511
00:21:45,149 --> 00:21:46,509
Is the flower seed nice?

512
00:21:46,509 --> 00:21:47,349
Yes.

513
00:21:48,269 --> 00:21:49,029
Dad.

514
00:21:49,029 --> 00:21:50,269
How dare you!

515
00:21:51,149 --> 00:21:53,069
Put all the prohibited items
on the table.

516
00:21:53,069 --> 00:21:54,269
Put it on the table.

517
00:21:56,109 --> 00:21:57,389
What nonsense book is this?

518
00:21:57,389 --> 00:21:59,109
Mr. Xie. It's not a nonsense book.

519
00:21:59,109 --> 00:22:00,509
It's a reference book.

520
00:22:00,509 --> 00:22:01,989
Basic Music Theory.

521
00:22:02,389 --> 00:22:03,869
Do you like music?

522
00:22:06,069 --> 00:22:06,909
Jiang Yimian.

523
00:22:07,389 --> 00:22:09,109
Should I transfer you to the art class?

524
00:22:09,389 --> 00:22:10,989
No, no need.

525
00:22:10,989 --> 00:22:12,189
I will confiscate it.

526
00:22:12,189 --> 00:22:13,109
Mr. Xie.

527
00:22:13,109 --> 00:22:14,269
You better study the textbook.

528
00:22:15,389 --> 00:22:16,389
Game console.

529
00:22:26,269 --> 00:22:27,189
Lin Xi.

530
00:22:33,789 --> 00:22:35,669
It seems they are focused on the study

531
00:22:36,029 --> 00:22:37,469
and they are not aware
the light is on.

532
00:22:38,709 --> 00:22:40,029
What are you doing?

533
00:22:42,149 --> 00:22:43,389
Hey, you.

534
00:22:44,629 --> 00:22:45,669
Mr. Xie.

535
00:22:47,149 --> 00:22:47,989
The lights are on.

536
00:22:48,469 --> 00:22:49,389
Great.

537
00:22:51,189 --> 00:22:52,109
What are you up to?

538
00:22:53,429 --> 00:22:54,909
Mr. Xie, I'm teaching her

539
00:22:54,909 --> 00:22:56,109
this question.

540
00:22:57,469 --> 00:22:59,149
I've tried it many times.

541
00:22:59,149 --> 00:23:00,469
But it's still wrong.

542
00:23:00,469 --> 00:23:01,749
Oh, you're studying.

543
00:23:03,789 --> 00:23:05,509
This question is quite difficult.

544
00:23:08,109 --> 00:23:09,429
Look at them.

545
00:23:09,909 --> 00:23:11,469
You should learn from them.

546
00:23:11,469 --> 00:23:12,509
They are so focused

547
00:23:12,509 --> 00:23:13,469
on the study.

548
00:23:13,469 --> 00:23:15,189
Look at yourself.

549
00:23:15,189 --> 00:23:15,709
When I was away,

550
00:23:15,709 --> 00:23:17,069
look what you've done.

551
00:23:17,069 --> 00:23:17,949
You study knowledge

552
00:23:17,949 --> 00:23:19,269
for your own good.

553
00:23:23,189 --> 00:23:24,149
Please study well.

554
00:23:27,189 --> 00:23:27,909
Give it to me.

555
00:23:28,909 --> 00:23:29,669
Surrender it.

556
00:23:31,429 --> 00:23:32,389
Surrender it.

557
00:23:38,789 --> 00:23:39,829
What are you laughing at?

558
00:23:40,429 --> 00:23:41,989
You are in grade two now.
Don't act like a child.

559
00:23:58,269 --> 00:24:00,229
I left my ticket in the book.

560
00:24:06,109 --> 00:24:07,349
What do I do now?

