00:26:36,949 --> 00:26:38,229
every day

611
00:26:38,229 --> 00:26:39,509
in order to achieve 130 marks

612
00:26:39,509 --> 00:26:40,669
before the music festival.

613
00:26:40,909 --> 00:26:42,029
