in disguise.

620
00:26:54,789 --> 00:26:56,029
Perhaps something good will happen

621
00:26:56,029 --> 00:26:57,349
if you can't achieve the score.

622
00:26:57,989 --> 00:26:58,789
That's right.

623
00:26:58,989 --> 00:27:00,309
