638
00:27:45,869 --> 00:27:46,589
Mianmian.

639
00:27:46,949 --> 00:27:48,109
Actually, the music festival...

640
00:27:48,109 --> 00:27:48,989
Lin Xi,

641
00:27:49,629 --> 00:27:51,149
