00:28:02,309 --> 00:28:03,189
And Chen Mo,

647
00:28:04,029 --> 00:28:05,389
you are obsessed with physics.

648
00:28:07,909 --> 00:28:08,629
Xie Ang.

649
00:28:09,869 --> 00:28:11,229
You have been wanting to start up
a business.

650
00:28:13,989 --> 00:28:15,509
Everything you like

651
