00:29:31,469 --> 00:29:32,069
I think

671
00:29:32,709 --> 00:29:34,109
we should help her with the revision.

672
00:29:35,669 --> 00:29:36,909
Are you sure?

673
00:29:37,949 --> 00:29:39,109
If she is given hope now,

674
00:29:39,509 --> 00:29:40,909
she will be even more disappointed

675
