677
00:29:44,949 --> 00:29:46,069
to enhance herself to be up to mark

678
00:29:46,509 --> 00:29:47,829
for the beautiful hope

679
00:29:47,829 --> 00:29:48,829
that is to meet them.

680
00:29:49,269 --> 00:29:50,909
She is trying really hard
to improve herself.

681
00:29:51,189 --> 00:29:52,229
Don't you think

682
00:29:52,229 --> 00:29:53,349
she's brave?

683
00:29:57,429 --> 00:29:58,349
We all know

684
00:29:58,949 --> 00:30:00,069
that we should go all out

685
00:30:00,309 --> 00:30:01,829
for something we yearn for.

686
00:30:02,109 --> 00:30:03,829
Nothing can halt us.

687
00:30:05,269 --> 00:30:05,949
So,

688
00:30:06,429 --> 00:30:08,109
regardless of whether the music festival
is fake or not,

689
00:30:09,109 --> 00:30:10,349
we shall stay beside her

690
00:30:10,349 --> 00:30:11,709
when she is pursuing her goal.

691
00:30:12,269 --> 00:30:13,989
Isn't that more important?

692
00:30:19,629 --> 00:30:20,389
