for Jiang Yimian.

694
00:30:25,189 --> 00:30:25,989
Wait for me, Xie Ang.

695
00:30:28,109 --> 00:30:28,949
I'm in too.

696
00:30:30,269 --> 00:30:30,949
And me.

697
00:30:32,349 --> 00:30:33,229
We will join too.

698
00:30:35,829 --> 00:30:36,589
I didn't know

699
00:30:37,349 --> 00:30:38,309
the East Gate Squad

700
00:30:38,309 --> 00:30:39,629
is so united.

701
00:30:39,869 --> 00:30:40,629
Of course.

