720
00:32:32,869 --> 00:32:33,949
the ticket is still a fake one.

721
00:32:33,949 --> 00:32:35,349
It's still a false hope.

722
00:32:35,509 --> 00:32:37,509
Here, check it yourself.

723
00:32:40,909 --> 00:32:42,629
132 marks.

724
00:32:42,749 --> 00:32:43,269
Thank you, Mr. Xie.

725
00:32:43,269 --> 00:32:44,509
Here. Take this back.

726
00:32:44,589 --> 00:32:45,549
Thank you, Mr. Xie.

727
00:32:45,549 --> 00:32:46,989
Thank you so much.

728
00:32:48,709 --> 00:32:50,629
I got 132 marks.

729
00:32:51,349 --> 00:32:52,949
I got 132 marks.

730
00:32:53,109 --> 00:32:54,469
Thank you, everyone.

731
00:32:54,469 --> 00:32:55,389
