758
00:34:04,469 --> 00:34:05,229
Well,

759
00:34:05,509 --> 00:34:07,589
I just play it for fun at home.

760
00:34:07,589 --> 00:34:09,509
I have never collaborated with someone
in the band.

761
00:34:10,909 --> 00:34:12,149
And you too, Lin Xi.

762
00:34:12,589 --> 00:34:14,349
Didn't you learn to play the drum
for three years?

763
00:34:15,109 --> 00:34:16,469
