right?

781
00:35:20,309 --> 00:35:21,389
Yes, they are.

782
00:35:21,389 --> 00:35:23,669
However, we can't master the instrument

783
00:35:24,549 --> 00:35:26,429
in such a short period.

784
00:35:26,869 --> 00:35:28,909
Take your time to learn it.

785
00:35:28,909 --> 00:35:30,469
You will do better one day.

786
00:35:31,509 --> 00:35:32,909
We are lacking skills

787
00:35:32,909 --> 00:35:34,829
and this song is too hard for us.

788
00:35:34,829 --> 00:35:36,229
As for the ensemble in the last part,

789
00:35:36,229 --> 00:35:37,709
I suppose we need three months
to practice.

790
00:35:38,709 --> 00:35:39,829
Not really.

791
00:35:40,149 --> 00:35:40,909
Well.

792
00:35:40,909 --> 00:35:42,069
