825
00:37:01,949 --> 00:37:03,269
What the hell is this?

826
00:37:03,269 --> 00:37:04,149
We spent 200 yuan to reach here.

827
00:37:04,149 --> 00:37:04,549
Your ticket

828
00:37:04,549 --> 00:37:05,909
isn't printed with
the official seal, date

829
00:37:05,909 --> 00:37:06,869
and the address.

830
00:37:06,869 --> 00:37:08,069
What do we do now?

831
00:37:08,069 --> 00:37:10,469
We bought the ticket
from the official channel.

832
00:37:13,349 --> 00:37:15,309
Hello.

833
00:37:15,309 --> 00:37:16,109
What's going on now?

834
00:37:16,509 --> 00:37:18,069
