836
00:37:19,949 --> 00:37:20,949
What do you mean?

837
00:37:21,309 --> 00:37:21,869
How could it be possible?

838
00:37:21,869 --> 00:37:22,909
I even got the ticket with me.

839
00:37:22,909 --> 00:37:23,629
Police said

840
00:37:23,629 --> 00:37:24,749
it was the scammer who spread

